                Cream to the white. Sometimes with light reddish brown.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rightsub">
            <div class="inlineblock">
                <img alt="" src="../../Content/images/arrow2.png" />
            </div>
            <div class="rightsubtitle">
                Features
            </div>
            <div class="middleline">
                <img alt="" width="440" style="overflow: hidden; height: 2px;" src="../../Content/images/line3_middle.png" />
            </div>
            <div class="rightext2">
                Wood texture is close and uniform with good polishing. Sometimes it has light greenish
                gray mineral lines and easy to paint.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rightsub">
            <div class="inlineblock">
                <img alt="" src="../../Content/images/arrow2.png" />
            </div>
            <div class="rightsubtitle">
                Wood nature
            </div>
            <div class="middleline">
                <img alt="" width="440" style="overflow: hidden; height: 2px;" src="../../Content/images/line3_middle.png" />
            </div>
            <div class="rightext2">
                Moderate intensity, fine wood, dense, beautiful patterns, good gloss and wood grain
